================ localhost =================

Python 3:
python -m http.server

Python 2:	
python -m SimpleHTTPServer

localhost:8000

============ Virtual Environment ============
****** venv *******
python3 -m venv ~/venv/ENV_NAME

**** vritualenv *****
python3 -m virtualenv ~/venv/ENV_NAME
virtualenv -p python3 ~/venv/ENV_NAME
virtualenv -p python3 ~/venv/ENV_NAME --python=python3.7 (if python3.7 is installed)

***** run env ******** 
source ~/venv/ENV_NAME/bin/activate
windwos:
 call [path]/scripts/activate
 (or just [path]/scripts/activate)

****** end **********
deactivate


******* remove env ********
rm -rf PATH/to/foler




===========  Jupyter notebook themes ===================
 1. install jupiter notebook (linux,OS X,window common)
 (for virtualevn, activate virtual python first, and run command)
 pip install jupyter



 2. install jupyter themes
 pip install jupyterthemes


 3. change theme
 windows : [python path]/Scripts/jt.exe
 jt -l : show the list of themes

 $ jt -l
   chesterish
   grade3
   gruvboxd
   gruvboxl
   monokai
   oceans16
   onedork
   solarizedd
   solarizedl

 jt -t [theme name] : change theme
 jt -t onedork

 linux/mac : [python path]/bin/jt
 (:activate virtual python first, and run command)
 jt -t [theme name] :  change theme
 jt -l : show the list of themes

**** Font ****
jt -t onedork -f cousine

